Package: rgrassdoc
Type: Package
Title: Consult 'GRASS GIS' documentation in the RStudio viewer pane
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Valentin",
           family = "Lucet",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "valentin.lucet@gmail.com")
Description: A tool for easy viewing of the documention for 'GRASS GIS' (see 
    <https://grass.osgeo.org/>). Pages of the 'GRASS GIS' manuals found at 
    <https://grass.osgeo.org/grass78/manuals/> can be viewed within the Viewer 
    pane of 'RStudio', or be opened in the user's default browser. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
